  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:6",
      "text": "Pixel Variance（像素方差）",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:7",
      "text": "这是对 sampling 导致的 noise 的度量。",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:8",
      "text": "pixel variance 越高，图像看起来越 noisy。",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:11",
      "text": "variance threshold（方差阈值）",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:13",
      "text": "pixel variance threshold 越低，最终 render 越干净，但完成渲染所需时间也越长。一般来说，每当你把 variance threshold 减半，render time 就会增加到四倍。",
      "ascii_letters": 55,
      "cjk_chars": 36
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:17",
      "text": "Min Samples",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:18",
      "text": "Max Samples",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:19",
      "text": "Pixel Variance",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:23",
      "text": "Min Samples",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:24",
      "text": "Max Samples",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:25",
      "text": "Pixel Variance",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:26",
      "text": "使用这些 base settings，让我们启动一次 render。",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:33",
      "text": "How to choose a threshold?（如何选择 threshold？）",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:35",
      "text": "“我的 pixel variance value 应该设成多少？”",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:38",
      "text": "好消息是，由于 RenderMan Denoiser 非常擅长在保留 hair 和 surface imperfections 中细微细节的同时去除 noise，它已经让 Pixar 能够把大多数 production shots 的 pixel variance 提高到",
      "ascii_letters": 79,
      "cjk_chars": 38
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:41",
      "text": "既然知道 RenderMan denoiser 能为我们提供支持，我们就知道把 pixel variance 降到",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 20
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:44",
      "text": "然后再启动几次 render，每次提高 pixel variance，直到达到 rendering sweet spot：快速 render times，以及 denoiser 能够清理的可接受 noise 量。",
      "ascii_letters": 61,
      "cjk_chars": 28
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:48",
      "text": "Visualizing your samples（可视化你的 samples）。",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:51",
      "text": "RenderMan 有一个非常有用的 AOV，名为 Sample Count，可以把它添加到 render 中，并在 IT 中检查其 values，帮助你判断 renderer 正在哪里计算 samples。",
      "ascii_letters": 52,
      "cjk_chars": 35
    },
    {
      "item_id": "8253c1a53e:53",
      "text": "当你在 IT viewer 中用鼠标悬停检查这些 pixels 时，会看到该 pixel 精确的 “average samples per pixel”。",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 21
    }
  ],
